OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than
OL,4,Cexpected as Ofgem increases price cap
OL,6,FIn practice, most people will pay less
OL,7,Fto their energy suppliers in the
OL,8,Fspring and summer months, because
OL,9,Fhouseholds typically use less energy
OL,10,Fthen.
OL,12,F"We know that no price rise is ever
OL,13,Fwelcome, and that the cost of energy
OL,14,Fremains a huge challenge for many
OL,15,Fhouseholds," Ofgem Chief Executive
OL,16,FJonathan Brearley said.
