OL,3,CEnergy bills to rise by more than
OL,4,Cexpected as Ofgem increases price cap
OL,6,F"But our reliance on international gas
OL,7,Fmarkets leads to volatile wholesale
OL,8,Fprices, and continues to drive up
OL,9,Fbills, which is why it's more
OL,10,Fimportant than ever that we're driving
OL,11,Fforward investment in a cleaner,
OL,12,Fhomegrown system."
OL,14,FHe added that those worried about
OL,15,Fpaying their energy bills should reach
OL,16,Fout to their supplier: "Where
OL,17,Fpossible, switching or fixing tariffs
OL,18,Fnow could also help to bring costs
OL,19,Fdown and provide certainty over coming
OL,20,Fpayments," he said.
